@startuml
title Coach Generate Optimal Schedule
actor Coach
participant "Web App" as WA
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "App Server" as AS
database "Database" as DB

Coach -> WA: Generate schedule
WA -> API: Send schedule generation request
API -> AS: Process schedule generation request
AS -> DB: Read team's schedule availability
DB --> AS: Availability data
AS --> API: Run optimization algorithm
API --> WA: Return generated schedule
WA --> Coach: Display schedule options
@enduml